      - text: "I completed the three trials inscribed on the\nstone monument in the Lanayru region.\n\nAfter I collected three of Ruta's Emblems,\nthe monk told me to head to the Divine Beast.\nWhat awaits me there?\n\nHeading to the Divine Beast Vah Ruta is the only way\nto find out."
